20883, "views": 7530, "likes": 16, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075448573991526597", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075448573991526597", "text": "#India's ONGC plans to build 1.75 million ton national strategic oil reserve #oott https://t.co/nHGKgFnciR", "time": "05:14", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5298, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075449111227314555", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075449111227314555", "text": "#Russia's Ilsky oil refinery catches fire after drone attack, local authorities say\nA drone attack on Russia's Ilsky oil refinery in the Krasnodar region sparked a fire, while air defence units reportedly downed 376 Ukrainian drones overnight. #oott https://t.co/VyBfkRhSFw", "time": "05:16", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7449, "likes": 8, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075527641004953995", "url": "https://x.com/captsingh/status/2075527641004953995", "text": "⚓️ Tensions rising in the Strait. The ceasefire is fracturing, and the toll prospects are back on the horizon. Shipowners are already routing per Iran's stipulations—charting the path of least resistance to avoid the guns. Threat of military action looms. 🌊 #OOTT #Hormuz #Shipping", "time": "10:28", "author": "captsingh", "author_name": "Captain Singh, FICArb, 73K", "followers": 73131, "views": 590, "likes": 6, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2075537210716352704", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075537210716352704", "text": "Traffic slows through Strait of Hormuz as Iran tensions flare \nAnalyst says Iran has changed tactics\nIt is hard to track vessels as some turn off transponders, sources say\nEven before latest strikes, traffic was far below pre-war levels\n#oott https://t.co/mCeUVEZVQo", "time": "11:06", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3749, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2075537342933217600", "url": "https://x.com/DB_WTI/status/2075537342933217600", "text": "#OOTT #WTI \n#Bombing and a Tentative #Accord Didn’t Work. Does #Trump Have a Plan C for #Iran? https://t.co/0RML4PNIUL", "time": "11:07", "author": "DB_WTI", "author_name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12439, "views": 1000, "likes": 1, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075538231928717437", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075538231928717437", "text": "Tanzania’s Richest Man Pledges $100 Million for Dangote Refinery\n#oott https://t.co/k0pg6iurf0", "time": "11:10", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5550, "likes": 5, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075555879122837705", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075555879122837705", "text": "#Russia’s gasoline output covers 65% of demand after Ukrainian strikes, sources say\nMajor refineries halted after Ukrainian drone attacks\nRussia is boosting imports and has banned fuel exports\nOfficials say fuel shortages are a concern\nSupply may increase later in July\n#oott  https://t.co/YKJYY6Cxpr", "time": "12:20", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 11009, "likes": 15, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075560962124341339", "url": "https://x.com/VonburyResearch/status/2075560962124341339", "text": "SPR came down from 325.7M barrels the week before to 319.5M barrels in the EIA report for week ending July 3, 2026.\n\nAnother 6M barrels gone. \nSPR is still being drawn while the Middle East conflict shows no sign of ending.\n\n#OOTT #SPR #Geopolitics https://t.co/WaXyZbqEdx", "time": "12:41", "author": "VonburyResearch", "author_name": "Vonbury Research", "followers": 738, "views": 2461, "likes": 16, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["US inventories", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075574882335948996", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2075574882335948996", "text": "Haven't written a long Iran-centric post since all this started 4+ months ago. Guess its time..TLDR version: Iran dynamic will be a wild card for at least another 3 months, anything below $75/bbl WTI is too cheap, watch Hormuz, inventory, China. Read on for the thread! #EFT #OOTT", "time": "13:36", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 19026, "likes": 108, "replies": 16, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 58, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075574945548247523", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2075574945548247523", "text": "On energy lags S&amp;P point, I'll be very happy to be wrong as I'm as bullish about the sector as I've been in several years. But 30%+ of the S&amp;P500 refuses to be wagged by energy's 3%. Good luck out there everyone.I look forward to your observations on my comments above! #EFT #OOTT", "time": "13:36", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 2170, "likes": 19, "replies": 4, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075585080269930659", "url": "https://x.com/SpartaCommo/status/2075585080269930659", "text": "Crude stocks just posted their first build in 11 weeks.\n\nGasoline is drawing down too, but distillates are the real story: down 5 million barrels and now 12% below the 5 year average.\n\nWhy? Abhishek Kumar explains. \n\nWatch the full episode: https://t.co/snYZDwI4P0\n\n#oott #crudeoil #diesel", "time": "14:17", "author": "SpartaCommo", "author_name": "Sparta", "followers": 6127, "views": 783, "likes": 7, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075589265430626654", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2075589265430626654", "text": "Does anyone need a refresher on how to make diesel?\n\nHint: no hopium involved\n\n#oott", "time": "14:33", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 9845, "likes": 45, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 16, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075592584953532478", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2075592584953532478", "text": "In theory, oil inventories shud be negatively correlated to time spreads. Left graph (from my book) confirms it, but recently these correlations became positive !!! (right) with spreads not doing anything despite empty Cushing, highlighting the dominance of other factors. \n#oott https://t.co/3B4Nzi1", "time": "14:46", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 12344, "likes": 91, "replies": 6, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 45, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075623516402266514", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2075623516402266514", "text": "Oil coming out of the Straits of Hormuz probably peaked in the last week or two\n\nNext stop, tank bottoms! #OOTT", "time": "16:49", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 4668, "likes": 30, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075628472529989879", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2075628472529989879", "text": "Baker Hughes Rig Count 07/10\n\n+1 overall, no breakout btw oil and gas available yet @bakerhughesco \n\n#oott #crudeoil #bakerhughes #rigcount", "time": "17:09", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 2460, "likes": 20, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Shale/US production"]}}, {"id": "2075642119386218934", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2075642119386218934", "text": "We’re hearing tons of noise about the Omani corridor in the SoH,